[{"id": "8a659e09-5268-4cf5-8a56-2b79b1e0c32c", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: Hi. i just installed this writing studio? what's next?\nASSISTANT: Hey \u2014 welcome aboard.\n\nFirst thing: Lagoon is BYOK (bring your own key), so you'll need to connect a provider before anything works. Hit **Settings** (gear icon) and add an API key for one of these:\n\n- **Venice.ai** \u2014 privacy-focused, good uncensored models\n- **Together.ai** \u2014 solid variety, reliable\n- **Ollama** \u2014 fully local, no key needed if you've got it running\n- **Any OpenAI-compatible endpoint** \u2014 KoboldCpp, LM Studio, llama.cpp, etc.\n\nOnce that's done, you can start a chat right away, or go to **Characters** and create someone to write with.\n\nWhat kind of writing are you looking to do?", "embedding": [-0.04298076406121254, -0.11653447151184082, 0.03351446986198425, 0.002701809862628579, -0.08723026514053345, -0.015764635056257248, -0.020614642649888992, -0.023005956783890724, 0.017658328637480736, -0.03485923632979393, 0.012462077662348747, -0.05774085223674774, 0.004216535948216915, 0.025333192199468613, 0.0748802050948143, 0.025903070345520973, 0.06604627519845963, -0.057397324591875076, 0.03625233843922615, 0.02691204845905304, 0.03648822382092476, -0.013572354800999165, -0.006462434306740761, -0.013674942776560783, 0.03487039729952812, -0.046516064554452896, 0.030029498040676117, -0.018423188477754593, -0.032788243144750595, 0.011952310800552368, -0.04082684963941574, 0.03331677243113518, 0.03942662850022316, -0.04246135801076889, 0.12299185246229172, 0.050754446536302567, 0.005315900314599276, -0.02096310257911682, -0.08533092588186264, -0.08665286749601364, -0.016733044758439064, -0.06732335686683655, -0.019128670915961266, 0.08846035599708557, 0.06736668199300766, -0.1099172830581665, -0.03565334156155586, 0.009960058145225048, -0.0024509034119546413, 0.049636904150247574, -0.06619077175855637, -0.05979407951235771, 0.007993783801794052, -0.040673334151506424, -0.0634665